results.name: Wmns RS-Curve 'International Women's Day'
results.story: The PUMA women’s RS-Curve ‘International Women’s Day’ celebrates the annual observance with a vibrant palette and playful enamel lace jewels, one featuring ‘Boss Lady’ inscribed on a set of lips, the other displaying PUMA’s jumping cat logo. The lifestyle runner carries a breathable mesh upper with pastel-hued leather overlays and padded textile around the collar and heel. Bright crimson accents land on no-sew skins and a pebbled leather Formstrip. Lightweight cushioning arrives via an exaggerated polyurethane midsole.

results.name: Kiko Kostadinov x Wmns FN1-S Gel Nimbus 22 'Baltic Jewel'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Kiko Kostadinov x FN1-S Gel Nimbus 22 ‘Baltic Jewel’ updates the performance running shoe with revised tooling and a futuristic aesthetic. The seamless upper is constructed from turquoise-colored technical mesh with contrasting white tiger stripes and silver undertones throughout. A matching silver heel piece displays Gel Nimbus 22 branding. A gradient blend of red and green is applied to the FlyteFoam midsole, featuring Gel cushioning in the heel for superior shock absorption.

results.name: Wmns Gel MC Plus 'Sheet Rock Digital Grape'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel MC Plus 'Sheet Rock Digital Grape' brings back a ‘90s running shoe created by Shigeyuki Mitsui, the legendary ASICS designer also credited with developing the Gel Lyte 3. The upper is constructed from black textile with grey suede overlays and a contrasting pop of violet on the back heel. The same grey and purple color combination is applied to the sculpted foam midsole, featuring visible Gel technology in the forefoot and heel for improved impact protection.

results.name: Wmns FN1-S Gel Nimbus 22 'Stone Grey Blue'
results.story: The ASICS women’s FN1-S Gel Nimbus 22 ‘Stone Grey Blue’ feature vibrant accents on a refreshed version of the original Gel Nimbus 22. Bright blue tiger stripes enliven a seamless upper constructed from grey technical mesh with gold undertones. The metallic hue is repeated on the sneaker’s upper eyelets and a molded heel piece marked with Gel Nimbus 22 branding. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a FlyteFoam midsole with ASICS’ Gel technology in the heel.

results.name: Wmns Oslo Maja Archive 'White Black'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Oslo Maja Archive ‘White Black’ showcases an essential palette on a lifestyle sneaker inspired by the original Oslo-City, an archival low-top that made its worldwide debut at the 1952 Winter Olympics in Oslo. Mounted on a platform EVA midsole, the upper is constructed from crisp white leather with grey suede overlays at the toe and heel. Black suede Formstrips are contrasted by ‘PUMA Oslo’ stamped in metallic gold lettering on the lateral side.

Mercedes-AMG Petronas F1 x Wmns Mile Rider 'Black Byzantium'
Wmns Shamrock Kinvara 12 'St. Patrick's Day'
results.story: The Saucony women’s Shamrock Kinvara 12 ‘St. Patrick’s Day’ celebrates March 17 with playful graphics plastered across the interior and exterior of the lightweight running shoe. The emerald-colored mesh upper, covered in an all-over argyle print with four-leaf clover details, sits atop a matching green PWRRUN midsole streaked with gold. Inside the shoe, an additional nod to the fabled pot of gold takes the form of a gold-coin print on the interior tongue, collar lining and insole.

Nike Dunk Low Orange Pearl (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Orange Pearl’ offers a pastel colorway of the classic low-top, rendered in traditional color blocking in keeping with the shoe’s ‘80s roots. The upper carries a stark white base with contrasting overlays in a pale coral hue. Traditional Dunk details include a perforated toe box and a lightly padded nylon tongue marked with a woven Nike tag. The sneaker is supported by a two-tone rubber cupsole, equipped with a basketball-specific traction pattern made for pivoting.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Green Strike (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Green Strike’ features a color-blocked design that nods to the silhouette’s ‘80s roots. The primitive 8-bit computer graphics of that era serve as the inspiration for the sneaker’s vivid palette, which combines a white leather base with a yellow forefoot overlay, lime green Swoosh, crimson eyestay and periwinkle heel. Contrasting black hits make their way to the woven tongue tag and heel tab, both marked with classic Nike branding.

results.name: Wmns Ultra Triller 'White Angel Blue'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Ultra Triller ‘White Angel Blue’ highlights an abstract graphic print throughout a woven jacquard upper, reinforced with synthetic suede overlays and a molded heel clip. The sneaker’s laces are integrated into a PUMA Formstrip made with translucent TPU tubing that extends past and around the heel. A springy engineered Proplate works in tandem with a Profoamlite midsole, supported underfoot by a cored-out gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns NMD_R1 'Floral - White'
results.story: Developed in partnership with the female-led design agency, the Her Studio London x adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Floral’ pairs cushioned comfort with lush graphics. They take the form of a multicolor floral print on the sneaker’s signature three-stripes and molded heel patch, allowing the details to stand out against a stark white textile backdrop. The blossoms make a repeat appearance on the NMD’s trademark EVA plug, embedded in the lateral sidewall of the Boost midsole.

results.name: Wmns LQDCELL Method 'White Angel Blue'
results.story: The PUMA women’s LQDCELL Method ‘White Angel Blue’ features subtle pops of color on a performance training shoe built for high-intensity workouts. The form-fitting upper is constructed from breathable white mesh with a synthetic leather midfoot cage for lateral support. Turquoise accents include a raised PUMA wordmark and visible LQDCELL cushioning nestled in the heel of the full-length EVA midsole. A zone rubber outsole provides lightweight and durable traction.

Wmns NMD_R1 'Light Purple'
results.story: The adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Light Purple’ showcases a pastel finish throughout the knit textile upper, engineered to hug the foot in flexible, breathable support. Tonal three-stripes are accompanied by Trefoil branding hits at the tongue and molded heel patch. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, fitted with signature EVA plugs that maintain the sneaker’s two-tone color scheme. A semi-translucent rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

results.name: adidas Forum Low I Love Dance (W)
Scuderia Ferrari x Wmns Ridge Cat 'Black Rosso Corsa'
Her Studio London x Wmns Nizza Platform 'Floral'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Nizza Platform ‘Floral’ is drawn from a footwear and apparel collection developed jointly with the print design agency based in East London. Their take on the vintage silhouette features a hectic floral print throughout the lightweight textile upper, accented with contrasting white three-stripes and mounted on a platform vulcanized rubber midsole. ‘Her Studio London’ is inscribed on an EVA sockliner that delivers lightweight cushioning with every step.

results.name: Wmns Carina Untamed 'Snakeskin - White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Carina Untamed ‘Snakeskin’ adds fashion-forward style to a retro-inspired silhouette that takes its cues from classic ‘80s tennis shoes. The low-top is constructed from crisp white leather with a snakeskin-printed Formstrip and a silver PUMA wordmark stamped on the lateral quarter panel. The same metallic sheen is applied to the heel of the rubber midsole. A breathable mesh-lined interior combines with a SoftFoam+ sockliner to provide step-in comfort.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Superstar Bold 'Floral'
results.story: Dropping as part of a larger collection with the print design agency, the Her Studio London x adidas women’s Superstar Bold ‘Floral’ treats the shell-toed sneaker to a stylish makeover. Pristine white leather is utilized on the upper, accented with shimmering metallic gold three-stripes and a baroque multicolor floral print on the enlarged heel tab. The low-top sits on a platform sole, complete with an exaggerated herringbone tread on the rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Ultra Triller 'Black Metallic Gold'
results.story: Inspired by reductionist theory, the PUMA women’s Ultra Triller ‘Black Metallic Gold’ uses tooling that removes excess materials for ultra-lightweight cushioning. In addition to the negative space between the engineered Proplate and Profoamlite midsole, the sneaker’s durable rubber outsole features hollowed, cored-out construction. Up top, engineered woven jacquard is reinforced with a synthetic suede toe cap and molded heel counter. Laces are integrated into gold-tinged TPU tubing that forms PUMA’s signature Formstrip.

results.name: Wmns Ultra Triller 'Elektro Peach'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Ultra Triller ‘Elektro Peach’ treats the stylish running shoe to a monochromatic makeover, executed on a lightweight textile build reinforced with tonal synthetic suede overlays. An extended tongue is constructed from breathable mesh, while the signature Formstrip is made with translucent tubing that’s integrated into the lacing system. Responsive cushioning is provided by a springy Proplate and Profoamlite midsole, featuring negative space in between for reduced weight. A cored-out rubber outsole yields grippy traction.

results.name: Wmns Eris Fantasy 'White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Eris Fantasy ‘White’ delivers a pristine monochromatic colorway of a lifestyle silhouette that blends modern, minimalist style with aggressive tooling. The sneaker’s white leather upper is accented with a PUMA Formstrip made with a blend of stitched and perforated detailing. A molded polyurethane sockliner offers lightweight cushioning with every step. The matching white rubber midsole is partially wrapped for added durability and a street-ready aesthetic.

results.name: Wmns Gel Kumo Lyte 2 'White Pure Silver'
Scuderia Ferrari x Wmns Ridge Cat 'White Rosso Corsa'
results.story: Continuing a motorsport-focused collaboration begun in 2005, the Scuderia Ferrari x PUMA women’s Ridge Cat ‘White Rosso Corsa’ shows off a streamlined silhouette built low to the ground. The slip-on is constructed from white synthetic leather, accented with a Scuderia Ferrari badge and an embroidered PUMA Formstrip outlined in red. A CMEVA foam heel insert offers lightweight cushioning, while the rubber outsole is equipped with a rounded driver's heel for added grip.

results.name: Wmns Gel Kumo Lyte 2 'Black Graphite Grey'
Wmns LQDCELL Method 'Black Soft Fluo Yellow'
results.story: The PUMA LQDCELL Method ‘Black Soft Fluo Yellow’ updates the performance training shoe with a contrasting two-tone color scheme. The sneaker’s black mesh upper is fortified with a tonal midfoot cage that provides lateral support while also protecting the lacing system. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a Profoam midsole, made with high-rebound EVA and enhanced with visible LQDCELL technology in the heel. Underfoot, a zoned rubber outsole with forefoot flex grooves provides durable traction and a smooth ride.

Egle Zvirblyte x Wmns UltraBoost S&L DNA 'Setsubun'
results.story: Releasing as part of a footwear and apparel collection with the award-winning artist, the Egle Zvirblyte x adidas women’s UltraBoost S&L DNA ‘Setsubun’ updates the lifestyle runner with bold splashes of primary color. They enliven the molded midfoot cage, which bolsters a sock-like Primeknit upper made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester. The sneaker’s full-length Boost midsole is supported underfoot by adidas’ Torsion bar and a grippy Continental rubber outsole.
